procedure
1) Install Ros(melodic version), MAVLink, Gazebo
2) Build PX4 firmware
3) Install QGroundControl
4) execute

1) Install Ros, MAVLink, Gazebo

	open terminal and 
	//
	wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PX4/Devguide/master/build_scripts/ubuntu_sim_ros_melodic.sh
	source ubuntu_sim_ros_melodic.sh
	cd catkin_ws
	catkin make
	//

2) Build PX4 firmware

	open terminal and
	//
	cd ~
	mkdir src
	cd src
	git clone https://github.com/PX4/Firmware.git
	cd Firmware
	make px4_sitl jmavsim
	//

3) Install QgroundControl
	go to link: 
	https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/qgroundcontrol/builds/master/QGroundControl.AppImage

	open terminal and
	//
	sudo usermode -a -G dialout $USER
	sudo apt-get remove modemmanager -y
	sudo apt install gstreamer1.0-plugins-bad gstreamer1.0-libav gstreamer1.0-gl -y


	logout and login again and

	open terminal and
	//
	chmod +x ./QGroundControl.AppImage
	//

4) executate 

	open terminal and
	//
	./QGroundControl.AppImage
	//

	open other termianl and
	//
	cd src/Firmware/
	sudo make px4_sitl
	//
